@startuml ZID-Automat_Controller-ZIDAutomat

package "ZID-Automat Controller" {
  [Main Controller] as MainCtrl
  [Borrow Manager] as BorrowMgr
  [Data Logger] as DataLog
  [QR Code Reader] as QR
  [Item Ejection Mechanism] as Eject
  [LCD Screen] as LCD
  [LED Strip] as LED
  [Configuration] as Config
}

cloud "Backend System" {
  [Backend API] as API
}

MainCtrl --> BorrowMgr : manages
MainCtrl --> DataLog : uses
MainCtrl --> Config : loads

BorrowMgr --> QR : reads
BorrowMgr --> Eject : controls
BorrowMgr --> LCD : updates
BorrowMgr --> LED : controls
BorrowMgr --> API : communicates

DataLog --> API : sends logs

API --> BorrowMgr : validates/provides data

@enduml